{"about_the_game":"Experience the fusion of Racing and Skateboarding \u2013 with a touch of Chaos!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Skate &amp; Car Physics</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999130/extras/TestGif.gif?t=1716626126\" /><br>It's a car? It's a skate? Nope... It's both! Flex Riders introduces a unique vehicle physics that combines skateboarding and racing. <br>Perform stunning tricks like flips, 360s, grinds, manuals, wallrides, and fakies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Combat Items</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999130/extras/FR_Gif_Items.gif?t=1716626126\" /><br>Unleash mayhem with an arsenal of combat items earned through daring stunts. <br>Chain these items together to create spectacular combos that leave your opponents in the dust.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Local Split Screen &amp; Online Multiplayer</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999130/extras/FR_Gif_Split.gif?t=1716626126\" /><br>Challenge your friends in split-screen battles or take on opponents from around the world in online game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Procedural Race Track</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999130/extras/FR_Gif_Maps.gif?t=1716626126\" /><br>Every round, the map changes! <br>Race tracks are randomly generated for maximum replayability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Score System</strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999130/extras/FR_Gif_Score.gif?t=1716626126\" /><br>Winning isn't just about crossing the finish line first in Flex Riders. <br>Score points by taking down opponents or pulling off the most impressive tricks.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Inno